---
title: Smart Apricot-Mustard Pork Tenderloin with Clementine, Radish and Goat Cheese Salad
description: Juicy clementines, marinated radishes and tangy goat cheese are the star players of a hearty salad that accompanies pork tenderloin topped with a sweet and savoury apricot-mustard sauce.
